# About page or article
    If you want to display it in the header bar, you need to add a page, and if you want to display new content in the News page, you need to add an article



# How to Add Page
    Log in to wordpress and open the page TAB on the left. Click Add Page button


# How to Add Article/News
    Log in to the wordpress background and open the page TAB on the left. Click the Post button
